text: Ishq Pashmina is an Indian romantic movie. It stars Bhavin Bhanushali, Zarina Wahab, Malti Chahar and Brijendra Kala. Written and directed by Arvind Pandey. == Cast == * Bhavin Bhanushali * Zarina Wahab * Malti Chahar * Brijendra Kala * Kainat Arora * Gaurika Mishra * Vijay Mishra * Yash Chaurasia * Vikram Sharma * Ashna Soni == References == ==Other websites== * Category:2020s Indian movies
